{"tid":556591,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"窗口式浴室寶係終極垃圾","createTime":"2018-02-10T14:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T04:40:40.000Z","uid":52068,"like":48,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4bb6eb8a17e2a331d9014b23cfc1a9f2827cde","tid":556591,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟廚房個抽氣扇積左勁多油煙，冬天啲油煙凝住個抽氣扇根本就喐唔撚到。咁我呀媽就叫我老豆換換左佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，我老豆就去買抽氣扇。點知買完翻黎，買多左個浴室寶，順便換埋廁所個抽氣扇<img src=\"https://www.price.com.hk/space/product/240000/240018_zdkjej_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fproduct%2F240000%2F240018_zdkjej_0.jpg&h=0756a9b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ngiggas GR-88 就千五蚊左右<br />\n<br />\n一開始心諗：哇正有新野用，用用下就覺得唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開換氣模式沖涼，沖完成個廁所啲水蒸氣多到同北京啲能見度冇分別<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>根本就抽唔撚到氣</strong></span></span><br />\n研究之後就發覺佢個設計極之on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/221533_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F221533_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=71f45390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲生風吹入黎之後，即刻就抽翻出去，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">有撚用咩屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/222336_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F222336_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG&h=90d9aebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你又唔俾我淨開抽風，一開就要抽風吹氣同時開<br />\n<br />\n到我屋企人全部沖曬涼之後，塊牆濕曬，天花板啲水好似落雨咁滴落黎，真係乜野味都冇曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算係以前春天都未試過咁，更何況依家相對濕度50%都冇<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/32/Mama.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070110222122\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F32%2FMama.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070110222122&h=13ea647d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暖氣功能更加係垃圾<br />\n沖緊個時開，啲水蒸氣多到我都怕舊野會唔會漏電，再透過空氣中嘅水蒸氣電撚死我<br />\n沖完個時開，根本成間廁所已經暖曬，開=冇用<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/3c/490deb1464cad.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091101140604\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F3c%2F490deb1464cad.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20091101140604&h=87db03e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奉勸各位，唔好換窗口式浴室寶（天花式未用過，唔講），用翻最簡單幾百蚊個隻重好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">正垃圾<br />\n唉！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://m.popkey.co/c30557/O9Aek.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.popkey.co%2Fc30557%2FO9Aek.gif&h=a6661d7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdaa8ca6042c323bdc66eea9ff7354b8fefad103","tid":556591,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得個重點係個隔塵網好多呢類浴室寶都唔畀你洗，<br />\n只準用吸塵機吸塵，好似話洗咗唔知會影響啲咩潔淨效能"},{"pid":"322e7312b4367d6fa99377589f824d8726f9fded","tid":556591,"uid":996,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"我老母又係係咁投訴呢嚿嘢冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1d23b92b8875e041fa9fa33796350251c65747","tid":556591,"uid":25424,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"人人都話論抽氣能力，根本細抽氣扇都勁過佢n倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fdf94e78cd4917538d0b1032069fa6167ec627","tid":556591,"uid":34213,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"但冷空氣向下沉啵<br />\n<br />\n至多話抽風廢。"},{"pid":"4289c1edb0965101a7cd7c82d4c07f280c1e4c24","tid":556591,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"我本來想買隻黎孝敬阿媽<br />\n係牌子問題定所有都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0b823bee66ddb5c3c1da8c53dafc171c83c93b","tid":556591,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"求推介<br />\n主要想抽濕"},{"pid":"d9ca2cca6bd1bcf009647a12a543c60f809b2736","tid":556591,"uid":78574,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"我隻panasonic純吹暖風唔錯喎<br />\n唔好買d雜牌啦"},{"pid":"bbac37b53e091e1531bd5c7deb5a41eb6e61a0f1","tid":556591,"uid":87780,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"天花式一樣冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abccabef4c31a0cc29118c4a397ee8d006d02a63","tid":556591,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9ca2cca6bd1bcf009647a12a543c60f809b2736","tid":556591,"uid":78574,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"我隻panasonic純吹暖風唔錯喎<br />\n唔好買d雜牌啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"最大問題係抽風廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5014cc647ecf42df5ff004338e20c6f1adb64a","tid":556591,"uid":52068,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4289c1edb0965101a7cd7c82d4c07f280c1e4c24","tid":556591,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"我本來想買隻黎孝敬阿媽<br />\n係牌子問題定所有都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"多啲陪兩老飲茶算啦"},{"pid":"a885e920d418790832311977534d43d495cb8748","tid":556591,"uid":2772,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"廢人買廢牌係咁<br />\n根本唔應該視呢d廢牌為選擇<br />\n<br />\n買電器貪平中伏係抵死"},{"pid":"62c8ed219489a440fce734e4000f6e3d7f1808f0","tid":556591,"uid":9153,"like":0,"dis